data.description: WOW..just WOW! This is the house you have been waiting for. On a premium street in Tuckerton Beach this home has million-dollar amenities for a fraction of the price. Not to mention a new bulkhead & dock. Everything has been freshly renovated using high-end materials & a local top contractor. This home offers 4 bedrooms including a lavish Master, two luxurious bathrooms, an outside shower, a two-tone custom kitchen, waterproof/scratch resistant Bruce flooring in the main living areas & more. This amazing custom kitchen has custom cabinets, quartz countertops, a sea glass backsplash, stainless steel appliances, large center island, beachy lighting fixtures finished off w/ a spacious eating area. The bathrooms offer high-end tiling, furniture grade vanities & solid surface counters & more!
